{"tid":1912683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【美心伍家】主席兒子拖欠維修工程尾數，23工人堵路","createTime":"2020-03-06T08:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T13:59:45.000Z","uid":202464,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e3cc14458bcecea5ed912c5789167061fa04c156","tid":1912683,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T08:58:12.000Z","msg":"今早8時半左右，23名工人代表搬來沙包堵塞屋苑的車輛出入口，又展示橫額「康苑法團主席霸道扣血汗錢」。現任大廈法團主席伍威達，是美心集團主席伍沾德的兒子，工人多次要求與他對話，但也不獲理會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裝修判頭黃先生稱，屋苑於2017年進行大維修，整項工程費用共計億元；工程於去年中完成，惟有人要求500萬元尾數以三折埋單，工程公司拒絕，即不肯簽署支票支付尾數。"},{"pid":"da50c048229755dbdef9e09a3af656c105b48768","tid":1912683,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4086df7969f821c78ff3aa5f1ab663d135b5dd3","tid":1912683,"uid":204887,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:02:47.000Z","msg":"5m 都俾唔起 肉酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa28bfa83f778e7897e61beec7518102132237c1","tid":1912683,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d4086df7969f821c78ff3aa5f1ab663d135b5dd3","tid":1912683,"uid":204887,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:02:47.000Z","msg":"5m 都俾唔起 肉酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:03:13.000Z","msg":"無話唔畀，三折找數之嘛"},{"pid":"7f25943881af7de9e8fce4167ba9105cfe6300e2","tid":1912683,"uid":144541,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:06:01.000Z","msg":"打陣地係送頭，工人應該快閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f1570b2ef0420e10585a093969af6783ba9fd4","tid":1912683,"uid":294182,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:08:38.